WEBVTT

00:01.198 --> 00:02.438
Previously on "The Path"...

00:02.439 --> 00:06.248
I need a good man on
the ground in Milton.

00:06.249 --> 00:07.268
It's in Delaware.

00:07.269 --> 00:09.268
Oh, okay.

00:09.269 --> 00:10.358
He's been seeing an IS girl.

00:10.359 --> 00:11.458
I'm sorry. I'll offset.

00:11.459 --> 00:13.308
Does this mean you've been seeing her

00:13.309 --> 00:14.408
and lying to us the whole time?

00:14.409 --> 00:16.268
They need our help.

00:16.268 --> 00:17.288
They'll find someplace else to go,

00:17.289 --> 00:18.288
but it might take a couple days.

00:18.289 --> 00:19.458
Okay.

00:19.459 --> 00:21.358
I spoke with my dentist,
and he needs a receptionist.

00:21.359 --> 00:23.238
I could do that. I
could be a receptionist.

00:23.239 --> 00:24.408
Jason called me.

00:24.409 --> 00:26.428
He was inquiring about a
clinical test we're running here

00:26.429 --> 00:28.398
for fourth stage pancreatic cancer.

00:28.399 --> 00:29.448
He wanted to buy the drug.

00:29.449 --> 00:31.388
Well, did he say who it was for?

00:31.389 --> 00:34.228
No, but it must have been
for a person with means.

00:34.229 --> 00:36.428
How long has Steve been
away righting those wrongs?

00:36.429 --> 00:38.278
Months.

00:38.279 --> 00:39.338
What are we doing here?

00:39.339 --> 00:40.338
Looking for something.

00:40.339 --> 00:43.228
You check the balcony.

00:44.369 --> 00:45.418
Nothing.

00:45.419 --> 00:47.398
Steve would be incredibly excited

00:47.399 --> 00:51.308
about some special guests
that will be staying here.

00:51.309 --> 00:53.458
The sisters couldn't take the risk,

00:53.459 --> 00:56.428
but I told them, we will.

